	(text "Pin RXD is driven so this level shifter is strictly \nnot required and could be replaced by a R divider.\n\n3v into TXD is high enough for 5V logic.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 17.78 43.815 0)
		(effects
			(font
